oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Helen MacClosky
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: MacClosky, Helen; aviation; pilots; women;
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Original photo and newspaper clipping of Helen MacClosky. Newspaper clipping reads, "Feminine Record Holder - Helen MacClosky, holder of the international 100-kilometer women's speed record for light type airplanes. She likes to fly, dislikes reporters and cameramen."
oai_dc:dc.dc:contributor: Manuscript Collection processed by Laura Cunningham
oai_dc:dc.dc:format: black & white photo, 4 x 5 in., newspaper clipping, 4.5 x 5.5 in.
